      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone looking for reliable transportation on a budget. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some minor dings consistent with its age, and the interior shows moderate wear on the driver's seat and carpet. While it runs and drives safely, it will likely need some minor suspension work and a fresh set of tires in the near future. It\u2019s a dependable workhorse that prioritizes function over form.",
