    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting with my trusty ride, and it's been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been well-maintained, so it\u2019s totally ready for its next big adventure with you! It runs like a dream and looks great too. Perfect for someone who wants a reliable car that still turns heads. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
