    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that's been treated with a lot of love? This car is in great shape and ready for its next big adventure! It runs super smoothly and has been well-maintained, so you can drive away with total peace of mind. I've truly enjoyed every mile in it, and I'm sure you will too. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look or go for a test drive!",
