    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, offering precise engagement and a direct mechanical connection. The vehicle has undergone proactive maintenance, including a Vanos system refresh and rear subframe reinforcement, addressing common E46 chassis concerns. Suspension geometry remains true, providing the telepathic turn-in characteristic of the M-tuned MacPherson strut and multi-link setup. The limited-slip differential operates flawlessly, ensuring optimal torque distribution during spirited cornering. While showing light cosmetic wear consistent with its mileage, the powertrain remains potent and the structural integrity is excellent.",
